title: 113: The Amazon Haul Episode: August '20 Edition!
itunes:title: The Amazon Haul Episode: August '20 Edition!
description: In this episode, Lisa, Mikey, and Jamie try healthy foods found on Amazon! Finds like monkfruit-sweetened powdered peanut butter, protein puffs, low-carb pasta, and SO MUCH MORE! Plus, the gang tries a new veggie snack that Lisa gave a 10 out of 10! So don’t hesitate… Push play now! And when you’re done, click on over to our Foodcast page for a list of the products featured in the episode!
itunes:summary: We didn’t even have to leave the house for this haul! We clicked our way through Amazon on this week’s episode of Chew the Right Thing!
itunes:author: Lisa Lillien
